al/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係租金比埋個位你坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線 我真係唔明點做得住.......</blockquote><br />\n無計啦 都要蝕住做<br />\n老闆話見到d人辛苦完一日/半日黎食個飯<br />\n見到佢地個滿足樣就夠啦 錢ed野都係過眼雲煙<br />\n有能力咪回饋返社會"},{"pid":"7bb1ebe6cb5cafbc5d44b345e3adc20d6f6251b2","tid":364370,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"大家樂平時有炒開巴西豬扒期貨 果筆賺賺埋埋突左既咪回饋下社會"},{"pid":"d2f67318131897955aa7791be8f767797083fea7","tid":364370,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"你都唔知一個飯成本只係幾蚊雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1e5a30bb5719d7a6b3647287f95977bc0a4f95","tid":364370,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"好感恩"},{"pid":"5d3ceb29b6f0de855d641c36656d90a11d153727","tid":364370,"uid":25754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"食親大家樂都食到好重味,好重既人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f10af39ac088dbd8dc794120c29d40e39a76f8","tid":364370,"uid":108067,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"51717010b9485e3e803d06dad173b183002b859c","tid":364370,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"之前我成日屌大家樂加價<br />\n<br />\n但依家發覺佢算幾平<br />\n<br />\n起碼平過茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7de130f11ec4c477e4f9c12ae3407037e71ea78","tid":364370,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我成日屌大家樂加價<br />\n<br />\n但依家發覺佢算幾平<br />\n<br />\n起碼平過茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋸排鋸到渣渣聲先60 幾